---
<Layout title="Leonardo Castro Official Website, Portfolio and CV">
	<main class="box mx-auto px-2">
        <!-- header -->
        <header class="pt-32">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center space-x-8">
                <div class="bg-teal-600 rounded-full w-[120px]">
                    <img class="w-[120px] rounded-full" src="/assets/media/images/profile2.webp" alt="foto de perfil de Leonardo Castro">
                </div>
                <div class="flex-grow">
                    <h1 class="text-lg font-bold">Leonardo Daniel Castro Morales</h1>
                    <h2 class="text-md text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">Backend/Fullstack Developer</h2>
                    <h3 class="text-md text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-600 space-x-2">
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ldcmleo" class="hover:text-teal-600"><i class="nf nf-dev-linkedin"></i> Linkedin</a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/ldcmleo" class="hover:text-teal-600"><i class="nf nf-cod-github"></i> Github</a>
                        <a href="" class="hover:text-teal-600"><i class="nf nf-md-file_document"></i>CV</a>
                    </h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <section class="pt-12">
            <h1 class="text-lg">About me</h1>
            <div class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">
                <p>I am a self-taught Backend developer with focus on the creation of functional, simple and sustainable platforms. I am interested in both software engineering and its impact on the real world. I currently work with Go, APIS Rest design, microservices, and SQL databases.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="pt-12 pb-12">
            <h1 class="text-lg pb-8">Experience</h1>
            <div class="space-y-8">
            {
                ProjectsData.map((obj: any) => (
                    <Proyecto data={obj} client:load />
                ))
            }
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="pt-12 pb-12">
            <h1 class="text-lg pb-8">Education</h1>
            <div class="md:flex md:space-x-4">
                <div class="min-w-[120px]">
                    <span class="text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">2015 - 2020</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1>TecNM Campus Reynosa</h1>
                    <h2 class="text-md text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">Engineering in Information and Communication Technologies</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-md text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400 pt-8 pb-4">Certificates</h2>
            <Certificates />
        </section>
        <section class="pt-12 pb-12">
            <h1 class="text-lg pb-8">More about me</h1>
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="md:flex md:space-x-4">
                    <div class="min-w-[120px]">
                        <span class="text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">Birthday</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1>March 5</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:flex md:space-x-4">
                    <div class="min-w-[120px]">
                        <span class="text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">Languages</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1>Spanish - Native</h1>
                        <h2 class="text-md text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">English - B1</h2>
                        <h3 class="text-md text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">Czech - A1</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-md text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400 pt-8 pb-4">Other Projects</h2>
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="md:flex md:space-x-4">
                    <div class="min-w-[120px]">
                        <span class="text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">December 2020</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="w-[65px] h-[120px] bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat mb-2" style="background-image: url('https://www.megustaescribir.com/Images/COVER_MANUSCRIPT_106275');"></div>
                        <h1>Escritura creativa</h1>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">I wrote a short story called 'Father`, a story of reflection on life and interpersonal relationships. You can read it in <a target="_blank" href="https://www.megustaescribir.com/obra/106275/padre" class="hover:text-teal-600 transition-all ease-in duration-150 underline">megustaescribir.com</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:flex md:space-x-4">
                    <div class="min-w-[120px]">
                        <span class="text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">2023 - Present</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="w-[100px] h-[80px] bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat rounded-md mb-2" style="background-image: url('https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2NzQ5ODYzLnBuZw==/315x250%23c/VueAIQ.png');"></div>
                        <h1>RPG Cozy Game with <a href="https://ellen0ra.itch.io" class="hover:text-teal-600 transition-all ease-in duration-150 underline">@Ellenora</a></h1>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400">As a video game enthusiast, one of my favorite hobbies is the development of games. This project is a cozy role -playing game like Stardew Valley and Animal Crossing. It develops completely in the Godot Game Engine and is intended as a collaboration project with Ellenora. This simple project serves as a practice for me and a step towards fulfilling one of my dreams: officially publishing a game. Through this project, its objective is to refine my skills in games development, work in collaborative creativity and contribute a pleasant game experience to others.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="pt-12 pb-12">
            <h1 class="text-md text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400 pt-8 pb-4">Repositories</h1>
            <Repositories client:visible />
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>